sql:
SELECT name, calories, category
FROM desserts
WHERE calories = (SELECT MAX(calories) FROM desserts);

external_knowledge:
- This question assumes that a "reviewed dessert" is one that has at least one review associated with it; 
- The ranking of desserts by their average ratings is based on the assumption that higher ratings indicate better desserts; 
- The question does not specify a minimum number of reviews required for a dessert to be included in the results, as long as it has at least one review.
